name: pinel
description:
sometimes we just freak out, there's a lot to deal and we just can't
freaking out is a part of the healing process
–
as vezes algumas coisas simplesmente não dão pra lidar, surtamos e acho que faz parte do processo de evolução

This piece is from the collection "descartável", which is a audiovisual project that I discarded bad feelings and turned it into something that could heal me. The project addresses mental health issues, self knowledge and it was a opportunity to me to study animation. This is the 16th piece of the collection.

|||||| check the full project on https://qabri.eu
